LTV Corp said Pakistan ordered180 military trucks and spare parts worth 18.5 mln dlrs from AMGeneral, a unit of LTV's Missles and Electronics Group.    The company said the order includes 140 M809 Seriesfive-ton trucks and 40 M44A2 Series 2-1/2 ton trucks. They arescheduled to be delivered later this year. Reuter&#3;